<p><b>Michael Pollan</b> (born February 6, 1955) is an American author, columnist, activist, and professor of <a href="/wiki/Journalism" title="Journalism">journalism</a> and director of the Knight Program in Science and Environmental Journalism at the <a href="/wiki/University_of_California,_Berkeley" title="University of California, Berkeley">University of California, Berkeley</a>.<sup id="cite_ref-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-0" title=""><span>[</span>1<span>]</span></a></sup></p>
